---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us"
  description="Get in touch with the ZT1 Prep team. Questions about preparedness, content suggestions, or business inquiries welcome."
>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-stone lg:prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1>Contact Us</h1>

      <p class="lead text-xl text-stone-600">
        Have questions, suggestions, or feedback? We'd love to hear from you.
      </p>

      <h2>General Inquiries</h2>

      <p>
        For questions about preparedness, content suggestions, or general feedback:
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@zt1prep.com">hello@zt1prep.com</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        We read every email and do our best to respond within 2-3 business days.
      </p>

      <h2>Business & Partnership Inquiries</h2>

      <p>
        For business partnerships, sponsorship inquiries, or press requests:
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:partners@zt1prep.com">partners@zt1prep.com</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Content Corrections</h2>

      <p>
        Found an error or outdated information? We take accuracy seriously. Please let us know:
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:corrections@zt1prep.com">corrections@zt1prep.com</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        Include the URL of the page and details about the issue. We'll review and update as needed.
      </p>

      <h2>Before You Email</h2>

      <p>
        Many common questions are answered in our content:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>New to preparedness?</strong> Start with our <a href="/guides/start-here">Getting Started Guide</a></li>
        <li><strong>Building a bug out bag?</strong> See our <a href="/guides/bug-out-bag">Complete Bug Out Bag Guide</a></li>
        <li><strong>Questions about our recommendations?</strong> Check the FAQ section at the bottom of each article</li>
        <li><strong>Affiliate questions?</strong> Read our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Response Times</h2>

      <p>
        We're a small team, so please allow 2-3 business days for a response. During busy periods or natural disasters (when preparedness interest spikes), responses may take longer.
      </p>

      <p>
        We prioritize:
      </p>

      <ol>
        <li>Content corrections and accuracy issues</li>
        <li>Preparedness questions from readers</li>
        <li>Business inquiries</li>
      </ol>

      <hr />

      <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">
        Thank you for your interest in ZT1 Prep. We're glad you're here.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
